title: 14-Gauge 5 in. Trench Shovel with Fiberglass Long Handle
description: The Bully Tools 5 in. 14-Gauge Trench Shovel's blade measures 5 in. x 12.25 in. with a 45 in. handle. Tool measures 56.25 in. long. The Bully Tools Trench Shovel comes with a limited lifetime warranty that protects against defects in material and workmanship. Founded in 1994.
